The peace of the dead
Now that the magic herbs are in your possession, you can finally free the area around Dar-Leanos from the threat of the dead. To do so, you need to pour the herbal liqueur on the Altar in the middle of the Main Cemetery.
#subobj 1
Go to the main cemetery
The cemetery - the home of the undead - is located in the mountain ring south of the city.
#subobj 2
Oil the altar (with liquor!)
To appease the undead, douse the altar in the center of the graveyard with a tincture of Magic Herbs. Further the herbs will do their job.